data.name: saveUTF8ToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Always save the script file in UTF-8 encoding (otherwise used the Windows encoding page). Note: Macro descriptions can unreadable letters of comments if their script files or header files have a different encoding than UTF.

data.name: formatCodeToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Automatically formatting (inserting the missing spaces between arithmetic and logical operations) code of script when document is opened. Note: This will only work for script files and include files (.ssl .h).

data.name: pDefineStripComboBox.ToolTipText
data.value:
Definition of conditional compilation constant for preprocessor #if directives. You can add custom defines to file PreprocDefine.ini
Note: This setting used with Open Watcom or external MCPP preprocessor.
